Class VisitorAccessRef

java.lang.Object

fr.inria.verveine.extractor.java.visitors.refvisitors.VisitorAccessRef
public class VisitorAccessRef extends AbstractRefVisitor
A visitor that extracts accesses to variables. One difficulty is that variable are often SimpleName nodes But many other things are also SimpleName nodes (ex: name of an invoked method) So we need to differentiate them. The choice has been made to do this in the parent nodes of the SimpleName nodes
